# CiRA VMaker Client Environment Variables

# Thai TTS
# Thai text-to-speech is powered by PyThaiNLP Tacotron2 (ONNX Runtime Web)
# Model: https://huggingface.co/pythainlp/thaitts-onnx
#
# No configuration needed - models are downloaded automatically when first used
# Total model size: ~168MB (downloaded once and cached)
#
# The TTS runs entirely in the browser using WebAssembly, no server required.
